      <title>特斯拉 Optimus 机器人在 Cyber​​cab 活动中被远程操作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/tesla-s-optimus-robots-were-remotely-operated-at-cybercab-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，特斯拉公司在最近一次活动中利用人类远程控制其擎天柱机器人原型机的一些功能，旨在激发投资者对即将推出的产品的热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/tesla-s-optimus-robots-were-remotely-operated-at-cybercab-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 19:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌支持在 Kairos 协议中建造小型核反应堆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/google-backs-buildout-of-small-nuclear-reactors-in-kairos-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 旗下的谷歌正在投资开发下一代核电，支持一家正在建造小型模块化反应堆的公司，并同意在这些核电站开始向美国电网供电后购买能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/google-backs-buildout-of-small-nuclear-reactors-in-kairos-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 19:02:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tele2 任命 Xavier Niel 的 Play Poland 前首席执行官为首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/tele2-appoints-former-chief-of-xavier-niel-s-play-poland-as-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典电信运营商 Tele2 AB 于今年早些时候被法国亿万富翁 Xavier Niel 大量收购，该公司已选择 Niel 挑战者品牌 Play Poland 的前负责人担任其新任首席执行官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/tele2-appoints-former-chief-of-xavier-niel-s-play-poland-as-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 18:24:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
